irs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 478th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>350th Civil Affairs Command's 478th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 416th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>358th Civil Affairs Brigade's 416th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 426th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>358th Civil Affairs Brigade's 426th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 360th Civil Affairs Bde Flash.png|<center>[[360th Civil Affairs Brigade (United States)|360th Civil Affairs Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 412th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>360th Civil Affairs Brigade's 412th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 450th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>360th Civil Affairs Brigade's 450th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[United States Army Corps of Engineers|Engineer]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 27th Engineer Bn Flash.png|<center>[[20th Engineer Brigade (United States)|20th Engineer Brigade's]] (ENG BDE) [[27th Engineer Battalion (United States)|27th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 57th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 57th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 161st Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 161st Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 6th Bde Eng Bn Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]] (IBCT) 6th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 127th Bde Engineer BN Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division]] (ABN DIV), 1st IBCT's 127th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 37th Eng BN Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[37th Engineer Battalion (United States)|37th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 738th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT, 37th Engineer Battalion's 738th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 307th B