.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 21st MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 65th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 65th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 108th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 108th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 118th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 118th MP Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====Multidisciplinary Commands====\n<gallery>\nFile:JSOC flash.png|<center>[[Joint Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:USSOCOM flash.png|<center>[[United States Special Operations Command|Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCAFRICA flash.png|<center>[[United States African Command|Special Operations Command Africa]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCCENT flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Central]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCEUR flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Europe]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCKOR flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Korea]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCNORTH flash.png|<center>[[United States Northern Command|Special Operations Command North]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCPAC flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Pacific]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCSOUTH flash.svg|<center>[[United States Southern Command#Special Operations Command South|Special Operations Command South]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command (USACAPOC) beret flash.png|<center>[[United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command|US Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:USASOC flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:XVIII Airborne Corps BF.svg|<center>[[XVIII Airborne Corps]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Ordnance Corps (United States Army)|Ordnance]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:28 Ord Co beret flash.png|<center>[[52nd Ordnance Group (EOD)|52nd Ordnance Group]], 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 28th Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:722nd Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 722nd Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:767th Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 767th Ordnance Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Psychological operations (United States)|Psychological Operations]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 15th PSYOP BN Flash.png|<center>[[2nd Psychological Operations Group|2nd Psychological Operations (PSYOP) Group's]] 15th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US_Army_4th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[4th Psychological Operations Group|4th PSYOP Group]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 3rd PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 7th MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 7th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 8th MSIB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 8th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 301st Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>[[7th Psychological Operations Group|7th PSYOP Group]], 14th PSYOP Battalion's 301st Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 344th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 344th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 345th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 345th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US_Army_8th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[8th Psychological Operations Group|8th PSYOP Group]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Public affairs (military)|Public Affairs]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:Golden knights beret flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Recruiting Command|Marketing and Engagement Brigade]]'s [[United States Army Parachute Team|US Army Parachute Team]]</center>\nFile:US Army 49th Public Affairs Detachment Flash.png|<center>82nd Airborne Division's 49th Public Affairs Detachment</ce